description: A reference to a business process event. The reference can come from Workday ID.
Workday won't save this data in any Workday fields. You can use this field to copy the event name and identify which event you list in the Event Reference field.

Send_Back_Business_Process_Data.description: Specify the Reference ID for the business process step to which the business process will send back to.

validation.validation: You can’t send the event back to this business process step. Specify a valid business process step ID.
